<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UniEvent Secure | BAU</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #1e293b;
        }

        .navbar-custom {
            background: #0a2d6d;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }
        .nav-link-custom {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85) !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }
        .nav-link-custom:hover, .nav-link-custom.active {
            color: #ffffff !important;
        }

        .hero {
            position: relative;
            min-height: 500px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a2d6d 0%, #061c47 100%);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding: 60px 0;
        }
        .hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #0a2d6d, rgba(10, 45, 109, 0.3)), url('/bau-campus.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            clip-path: polygon(15% 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
            z-index: 1;
        }
        @media (max-width: 991.98px) {
            .hero::after {
                width: 100%;
                opacity: 0.15;
                clip-path: none;
            }
        }
        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 600px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            line-height: 1.15;
        }

        .featured-section, .guest-marketing-section, .faq-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        .event-card, .info-card {
            border-radius: 16px;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .event-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04) !important;
        }
        
        .info-card {
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .info-card:hover {
            border-color: #cbd5e1;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(10, 45, 109, 0.03);
        }
        .icon-circle {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background-color: rgba(10, 45, 109, 0.06);
            color: #0a2d6d;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .event-image-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border-top-left-radius: 16px;
            border-top-right-radius: 16px;
        }
        .event-image {
            height: 240px;
            width: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .badge-category {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 15px;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }
        .pill-badge {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: #475569;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .btn-action {
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .accordion-item {
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #ffffff;
        }
        .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
            background-color: rgba(10, 45, 109, 0.04);
            color: #0a2d6d;
        }
        .accordion-button:focus {
            box-shadow: none;
            border-color: rgba(10, 45, 109, 0.2);
        }

        .footer {
            background: #0f172a;
            color: #94a3b8;
            padding: 40px 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark navbar-custom sticky-top">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold d-flex align-items-center" href="/">
            <span style="letter-spacing: -0.01em;">UniEvent<span class="text-info">Secure</span></span>
        </a>
        
        <button class="navbar-toggler border-0" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#mainNav">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="mainNav">
            <div class="navbar-nav mx-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0">
                <a class="nav-link nav-link-custom active" href="/">Home</a>
                <a class="nav-link nav-link-custom" href="#events">Events</a>
                <a class="nav-link nav-link-custom" href="#features">Features</a>
                <a class="nav-link nav-link-custom" href="#faq">FAQ</a>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-link text-white text-decoration-none fw-semibold px-3">Login</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-light btn-action shadow-sm text-primary px-4">Register</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            
            <span class="badge bg-info text-dark fw-bold mb-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-pill">Guest</span>
            <h1>Discover Events Across Bahçeşehir University</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-white-50 leading-relaxed">
                Explore university workshops, conferences, seminars and student activities. Register securely, manage bookings and stay connected with campus events through UniEvent Secure.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <a href="#events" class="btn btn-info btn-action text-dark px-4 shadow">Browse Events</a>
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-action px-4">Create Free Account</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="featured-section" id="events">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="section-title mb-0">✨ Featured Events</h2>
            <span class="text-muted fw-medium d-none d-sm-inline">Showing live university updates</span>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <% if (typeof events !== 'undefined' && events.length > 0) { %>
                <% events.forEach(event => { %>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm event-card h-100">
                        <div class="event-image-wrapper">
                            <img src="<%= event.image_url || '/bau-campus.png' %>" class="event-image" alt="<%= event.title %>">
                            <span class="badge-category">Upcoming</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="card-body p-4 d-flex flex-column">
                            <div>
                                <span class="pill-badge">Free Entry</span>
                                <span class="pill-badge"><%= event.type || 'In-Person' %></span>
                            </div>
                            
                            <h4 class="fw-bold fs-5 mt-2 mb-3 text-dark leading-snug">
                                <%= event.title %>
                            </h4>
                            
                            <div class="text-muted fs-6 mb-4 mt-auto">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                    <span class="me-2">📍</span> <%= event.location %>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                    <span class="me-2">📅</span> <%= new Date(event.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'short', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' }) %>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary btn-action w-100 mt-2">
                                Login to Register
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="col-10 text-center py-5 mx-auto">
                    <p class="text-muted fs-5">No upcoming events listed right now. Check back shortly!</p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="guest-marketing-section bg-white border-top border-bottom" id="features">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center max-width-md mx-auto mb-5">
            <h2 class="section-title mb-2">Why Use UniEvent Secure?</h2>
            <p class="text-muted small">Streamlined ecosystem built specifically for Bahçeşehir University students and staff.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card info-card p-4 h-100 shadow-none">
                    <div class="icon-circle mb-3">🛡️</div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark">Verified Attendance</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Secure booking tokens guarantee your seat assignment directly within corporate lecture frameworks and seminar halls.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card info-card p-4 h-100 shadow-none">
                    <div class="icon-circle mb-3">⚡</div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark">Instant Allocation</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">No lines, no registration sheets. Book tickets dynamically in one tap and receive notifications instantly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card info-card p-4 h-100 shadow-none">
                    <div class="icon-circle mb-3">📊</div>
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark">Personal Calendar Log</h5>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Keep an archive of academic workshops, guest speaker notes, and community certificates under a single custom dashboard.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="faq-section" id="faq">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px;">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="section-title mb-2">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <p class="text-muted small">Everything you need to know about tracking events on campus.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion d-flex flex-column gap-3" id="guestFaqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item border-0">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button fw-semibold collapsed rounded-3" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq1">
                        Who can register for these events?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faq1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#guestFaqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body text-muted small">
                        All active BAU students, alumni, faculty members, and administrative staff can create an account and register for events hosted across our campus channels.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item border-0">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button fw-semibold collapsed rounded-3" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq2">
                        Are tickets or registration seat requests free?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faq2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#guestFaqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body text-muted small">
                        Most core university workshops, community tracks, and guest speaker seminars are completely free unless specified explicitly inside the description parameters.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item border-0">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button fw-semibold collapsed rounded-3" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                        How do I verify my booking at the door?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#guestFaqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body text-muted small">
                        Once you register and secure a seat, your profile creates an authorization confirmation voucher. Admins can view your registry details directly within the system portal at the entrance.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <p class="mb-1 fw-semibold text-white">Bahçeşehir University</p>
        <p class="mb-0 text-white-50">&copy; 2026 UniEvent Secure. Built for secure event infrastructure.</p>
    </div>
</footer>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>